    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Calibri';}\n.html-preview .a3 {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt; color: #000000; font-weight: bold;}\n.html-preview .Text {font-family: 'AntiquaUz'; font-size: 12pt;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">Васиятнома бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисидаги гувоҳнома олиш ҳақида </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-weight: bold;\">ариза</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#5}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">га</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#7}Ариза келиб тушган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йил</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мерос иши № </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#8}Мерос иши рақами </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#10}Ариза берувчининг онасининг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">онам</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; color: #ff0000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#11}Ариза берувчининг онасининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">нинг </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">(Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#12}Ариза берувчининг онасининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,<span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#13}Ариза берувчининг онасига паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#14}Ариза берувчининг онасига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">берилган) розилиги ва унинг иштирокида ҳаракат қилувчи </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">фарзанди </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#15}Ариза берувчининг манзили </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> томонидан </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">(Паспорт: </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#17}Ариза берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#18}Ариза берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">ИИБ томонидан</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 196.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#19}Ариза берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда берилган)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right; text-indent: 283.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; text-indent: 283.2px;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt; font-weight: bold;\">АРИЗА</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#2}Ариза тузилган жой</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#3}Ариза тузилган вақт </span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Менинг отам </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#21}Ариза берувчининг отасининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#22}Ариза берувининг отасининг яшаган манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида доимий равишда яшаб келиб, </span><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#23}Ариза берувининг отаси вафот этган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда вафот этди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Унинг ўлимидан сўнг мерос мол-мулк сифатида </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#24}Мерос-молк мулки жойлашган манзил </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> манзилида жойлашган уй-жой қолди.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#25}Васиятномани тасдиқлаган нотариал идора номи ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> нотариал идораси томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-26\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#26}Васиятнома тасдиқлаган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> йилда </span><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#27}Васиятнома рўйхатга олинган реестр рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> реестр рақами билан қайд қилинган васиятномага асосан марҳумнинг меросхўри мен </span><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> бўламан.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ўзбекистон Республикаси Фуқаролик кодексининг 1142-моддасига асосан юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка нисбатан мажбурий улуш ҳуқуқига эга бўлган меросхўрлар йўқ.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Менга юқорида кўрсатилган мерос мол-мулкка нисбатан васиятнома бўйича меросга бўлган ҳуқуқ тўғрисида гувоҳнома беришингизни сўрайман.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Мен мажбурий улуш ҳуқуқига эга бўлган меросхўрларни яширганлик оқибатлари ва жавобгарлик ҳақида огоҳлантирилдим.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">Аризамга қуйидаги ҳужжатларни илова қиламан:</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">1. Марҳумнинг ўлими ҳақидаги гувоҳнома нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">2. Васиятнома.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">3. Туғилганлик ҳақида гувоҳномам нусхаси.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">4. Кадастр хизмати органидан олинган маълумотнома.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">5. Мерос қолдирувчининг уй-жойга эгалик ҳуқуқини тасдиқловчи ҳужжат.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#28}Аризага илова қилинаётган бошқа ҳужжатлар </span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 36.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">{#6}Аризани тасдиқлаган нотариуснинг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\"> ______________ Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 38px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">нинг шахси </span><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#18}Ариза берувчига паспорт берган ИИБ номи </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> ИИБ томонидан </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#19}Ариза берувчига паспорт берилган сана </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> йилда берилган </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#17}Ариза берувчининг паспорт серияси ва рақами </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> серия ва рақамли паспорт бўйича аниқланди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 38px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 38px;\"></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 38px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">{#16}Ариза берувчининг Ф.И.О </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>______________ Имзо</span></p>\n<p class=\"Text\" style=\" text-indent: 329.6px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman';\">М.Ў.</span></p>\n</div></div>",
